<i>noun</i>: 영안실 [영안실], 안치실 [안치실], 빈소 [빈소] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>영안실 [영안실]</dt><br>
<dd>mortuary</dd><br>
<dd>병원에서 시신을 보관하는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>The section in a hospital where dead bodies are kept.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>안치실 [안치실]</dt><br>
<dd>mortuary; morgue</dd><br>
<dd>병원에서 시신을 모셔 두는 방.</dd><br>
<dd>A room where dead bodies are kept in a hospital.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>빈소 [빈소]</dt><br>
<dd>funeral home; funeral parlor; mortuary</dd><br>
<dd>장례식장이나 상갓집에서 발인 전까지 관을 놓아 두는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place within a funeral home or a house in mourning where a coffin is kept before the burial or cremation of the dead.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>